Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:07.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sì.{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:13.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Gente, vi prego, ascoltatemi!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:16.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Domani mattina verranno \N{\i1}davvero{\i0} dei pirati ad attaccarci!{angy}
