Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:40.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Inseguitelo! Non fatelo scappare!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:51.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uomini, ben arrivati.{angy}
